This guide provides context for an LLM embedded in an IDE to generate **semantic, fully-clickable cards** using `shadcn-vue` componentst follows accessibility and semantic best practices based on [Easy Semantic Card-Link](https://ru.ariarzer.dev/tutorials/2022/easy-semantic-card-link.html).

