## âœ… Goal

- Use semantic markup (`<article>`, `<h3>`)
- Wrap the title in a single `<a>` tag that activates the entire card
- Use CSS pseudo-elements (`::before`) for full-area interactivity
- Allow nested independent links (e.g., author link)
- Use `shadcn-vue` card components for structure
- Style using Tailwind CSS utility classes

